{"title":"The Marker Employees on the Best Local Spots","url_friendly_name":"the-marker-employees-on-the-best-local-spots","date":"2016-07-01","short_description":"The saying goes, “It’s the people that make the place,”","blogimage":{"url":"/assets/images/marker-employees.jpeg"},"more_content":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The saying goes, &ldquo;It&rsquo;s the people that make the place,&rdquo; &ndash;one of the many reasons we are proud to have a great staff at The Marker. From catering to our guests, to keeping day-to-day activities moving seamlessly at the resort, having an exceptional team makes the job that much easier! Not only is our team incredible at making your stay at The Marker a welcoming one, they also know all the best local hot spots in Key West to make your stay a truly memorable one.&nbsp; Our spotlighted employees include:&nbsp; General Manager Sharka Takovich, Food &amp; Beverage Manager Shawna M. Allen, our Assistant Direction of Sales &amp; Marketing Megan Coccitto, and Front Office Supervisor Joesph Pfander.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></u></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">Sharka Takovich</span></u></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Title:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> General Manager</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Loved the Marker since:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> December, 2015</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What is the best part about working at The Marker? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Providing a memorable experience to all of our guests, along with finding ways to make anything possible for the guests, while working with a great team with a &ldquo;can do attitude&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What are your top local spots to recommend to guests to get a true taste of Key West?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.mallorysquare.com/\">Mallory Square</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &ndash;the </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.mallorysquare.com/sunset-celebration/\">Sunset Celebration</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> spot where you can also watch local musicians, street performers, and artists.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Where&rsquo;s the best place to get Key Lime Pie in Key West?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The key lime pie at our restaurant </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/drinks---dining/cero-bodega/\">Cero Bodega</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> or </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.blueheavenkw.com/\">Blue Heaven</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rsquo;s pie.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What&rsquo;s your choice Cero Bodega cocktail?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">White Sangria.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">Shawna M. Allen</span></u></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Title:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Food &amp; Beverage Manager</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Loved the Marker since:</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> April, 2016</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What is the best part about working at The Marker? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">My favorite part about working at </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/\">The Marker</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> is the people. I am a part of an amazing team of individuals and get to meet new people daily from all over the world.&nbsp; It is such a privilege to have the opportunity to enhance someone&rsquo;s vacation experience. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What are your top local spots to recommend to guests to get a true taste of Key West? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">I encourage guests to explore areas of the island besides Duval Street, I recommend brunch at </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.fireflykeywest.com/\">Firefly</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.galleonresort.com/tiki-bar-deli.htm\">Sunset at The Galleon</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.yelp.com/biz/white-tarpon-key-west-2\">The White Tarpon</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> and a boat ride to Sunset Key for dinner. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What&rsquo;s your choice Cero Bodega cocktail?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;(Our bartender) Agota makes the best Coconut Mojito!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Which do you prefer: Cuban coffee or standard brew? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/blog-details/a-taste-of-cuban-coffee-in-key-west/\">Cuban coffee</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> always, we make Caf&eacute; Con Leches in house that are to die for. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">If you could pick a song that embodies the spirit of Key West, what song would it be? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lB8Nkn3Xjes\">Toes by Zak Brown</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">Megan Coccitto</span></u></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Title: </span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assistant Director of Sales &amp; Marketing</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Loved the Marker since: </span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">May, 2015</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What is the best part about working at The Marker? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The special events we put on! I loved pool parties for Fantasy Fest, the </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/blog-details/the-21st-key-west-song/\">Songwriters Festival</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, and Brewfest. They all had a great vibe. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What are your top local spots to recommend to guests to get a true taste of Key West?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">I usually recommend </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.floridastateparks.org/park/Fort-Taylor\">Fort Zachary Taylor State Park</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, taking a paddleboard tour, and for dinner and drinks, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://thirstymermaidkeywest.com/#menu\">Thirsty Mermaid</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> and </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.yelp.com/biz/shots-and-giggles-key-west\">Shots &amp; Giggles</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Where&rsquo;s the best place to get Key Lime Pie in Key West?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.blueheavenkw.com/\">Blue Heaven</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What&rsquo;s your choice Cero Bodega cocktail?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">I am a big fan of the blueberry champagne cocktail.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">Joesph Pfander</span></u></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Title: </span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Front Office Supervisor</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Loved the Marker since: </span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">May, 2015</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What is the best part about working at The Marker? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">I have enjoyed many memorable moments at </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/\">The Marker</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> including </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/blog-details/the-21st-key-west-song/\">Songwriters Fest</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> and Fantasy Fest Pool Parties, along with the everyday fun of living and working on an island paradise at the end of the road!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">What is your favorite place to visit that&rsquo;s within walking distance of the resort?&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">For a &ldquo;mucho caliente&rdquo; experience &ndash; I love to visit </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.peppersofkeywest.com/\">Pepper&rsquo;s of Key West</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.&nbsp; They have hundreds of hot sauces and dipping sauces to sample!&nbsp; They encourage you to bring your own six-pack to cool your palate after you have picked you favorite sauces!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">Which do you prefer: Cuban coffee or standard brew? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">After working in Key West each day for more than a year &ndash; nothing makes you feel more at home on the island than a steaming bucci or </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/blog-details/a-taste-of-cuban-coffee-in-key-west/\">Cuban coffee</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.&nbsp; I believe I am officially addicted!</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">If you could pick a song that embodies the spirit of Key West, what song would it be? </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Nothing sums up Key West more than &ldquo;<u>Be As You Are&rdquo; by Kenny Chesney</u>. The opening chords take away all of your stress and soothe your worries in a perfect combination of a tropical melody that puts you in an instant &ldquo;island&rdquo; state of mind.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">You&rsquo;ve read what makes our employees love </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.themarkerkeywest.com/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">The Marker</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">, now it&rsquo;s your turn. Share your experience at our resort on social with </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/lovethemarker/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">#LoveTheMarker</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">, and you may be featured on our </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/themarkerresort/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Instagram</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">! Make sure to follow us on </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheMarkerResort\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Facebook</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheMarkerResort\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Twitter</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">, and </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/themarkerresort/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Instagram</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"> to keep up with all things resort life!&nbsp;</span></p>","Posted_by":"Admin","categories":null,"image":{"url":"/assets/images/marker-employees.jpeg"},"tags":[]}